#

Apple Cinnamon Toast

15 min
$2.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

gluten

Dietary Tags:

vegetariannut-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfastsnackeasysweet

Description

A quick and delightful toast topped with sweet, cinnamon-spiced apples and a hint of butter.

Ingredients

  • sliced bread: 2 slices
  • apple: 1 medium, cored and diced
  • butter: 1 tablespoon
  • brown sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: a pinch
  • vanilla extract: 1/2 teaspoon
